Thomas

There is a nested pseudo selector bug when using sort.

before using sort:
.ie7 {

    a:link, a:visited,
    a:active, a:hover {
        color: #333;
    }

    a:hover {
        background-color: #c7d1d6;
    }
}

After using sort:
.ie7 {
    a:link, a:visited,
    a:active, a:hoverr {
        color: #333;
    }

    a:hover {
        background-color: #c7d1d6;
    }
}

Note the double rr on hover.
